        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但她好像在享受这种新的感官似的，又想把它同其他的感觉联系起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还好吗？",
